title: #92Noon! JG/Stump The Snob/Kyle Brandt/Darrell Thompson/Dan Hayes/
description: Nordo in for PA with Justin Gaard hanging out for the first segment of the show to talk the now delayed Gopher 2020-21 football season.  NFL Network's Kyle Brandt, calls in to talk about his new podcast and intimate interviews with Aaron Rodgers & Kirk Cousins. Gopher great, Darrell Thompson, dives into the details of the delayed Gopher season.  Dan Hayes of The Athletic breaks down the Twins recent losing slump.  And of course, Matt Birk joins Nordo for the weekly Birk Bit.
